                <note rend="inline" type="source">File 417.00/27. 28.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Minister</gloss> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Managua</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1911-05-09">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 9, 1911</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Judge Schoenrich arrived at Corinto May 5. Moffat left Managua last Monday for
                    the United States.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Northcliff.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
